c. Thus, it challenges monolithic and provincial representations of the South as a provincial region distinct from the rest of the country.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aAmerican literaturey19th centuryxHistory and criticism. 4aAbolitionismus. 4aAntebellum. 4aSklaverei. 4aWilliam Gilmore. 7aHISTORY / Modern / General.2bisacsh  aAbolitionism.  aAntebellum.  aSlavery.  aWilliam Gilmore.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishz978311075408708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021z9783110753851oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831106926000 cprintz978311069222840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110692471zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110692471zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110692471/original  a978-3-11-075070-6 DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  a978-3-11-075072-0 DG Ebook Package English 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075408-7 EBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishb2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-GOA